orate with Nursing Director to ensure the unit is following proper standards and procedures Charge Nurse requirements This section should list the essential qualities of an ideal candidate. Include previous work experience, education or achievements that would be beneficial. And list any preferred hard and soft skills. Example Charge Nurse requirements Valid Nursing license Bachelor of Science in Nursing (BSN) preferred Exceptional interpersonal skills and ability to resolve conflicts professionally Previous experience in a leadership role 2+ Years recent nursing experience Strong attention to detail and ability to multitask Charge Nurse related job titles: Critical Care Charge Nurse Full-Time Charge Nurse, Surgery Charge RN RN Charge Nurse RN Charge Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
